## Support

For issues or questions:
1. Check database tables exist: `sqlite3 data/skills.db .tables`
2. Verify sync endpoint: `curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/sources/sync -d '{"sourceId":2}'`
3. Review logs for sync errors
4. Confirm GitHub repo is public (or token has access)
